    <content>&lt;P&gt;You could just create an on-device entity -- no need to define all the fields -- and store an object in the entity. The rest depends on what needs to happen next in your requirement.&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1739256496311.png" style="width: 675px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/224574iF77CB2993028D9DD/image-dimensions/675x457?v=v2" width="675" height="457" role="button" title="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1739256496311.png" alt="Dan_Wroblewski_0-1739256496311.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
